result.title: CGI Animated Short Film: "Just Add Water" by Angela Colvin | CGMeetup
result.description:
CGI 3D Animated Short Film: Just Add Water Animated Short Film by Angela Colvin at Ringling College of Art and Design. Featured on CGMeetup http://www.cgmeetup.com/project/just-add-water-animated-short-film-by-angela-colvin 

With the help of a magic “Grow Your Own Unicorn” kit and a single drop of water, a majestic unicorn companion is minutes away from fulfilling the rest of eight-year-old Chelsea’s life. When the process exceeds Chelsea’s patience limits, she improvises, resulting in everything she never wanted.

An impatient girl gets the ultimate gift: Her very own unicorn. However, this unicorn is not what she expected.

Directed by Angela Colvin; Responsible for all aspects.
